South Africa Should Start Nuclear Procurement Next Year, Business Day Says

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-05-20T05:13:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-20/south-africa-should-start-nuclear-procurement-next-year-business-day-says.html
South Africa  needs to start its
nuclear program by 2012 so it can meet its target of producing
from its next plant by 2030, Johannesburg-based Business Day
reported, citing Energy Minister Dipuo Peters.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
